com.emc.storageos.model.auth

Class AuthnProviderRestRep

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.emc.storageos.model.DataObjectRestRep
      • com.emc.storageos.model.auth.AuthnProviderRestRep

  • public class AuthnProviderRestRep
extends DataObjectRestRep
    Class that encapsulates the REST representation of a Authentication provider profile. It also allows conversion from a AuthnConfiguration data model object.
